    "name": "ETH-Liq-COLL-PROT-time-2",
    "description": "DeFi ETH Collateral Treasury — Complete Balance Sheet Tracking\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nINITIAL POSITION:\n  ETH Holdings: 10.0 ETH @ $3,000 = $30,000\n  USD Cash: $0 (will borrow $9,000)\n  Net Worth: $30,000\n\nLOAN STRUCTURE:\n  Collateral Deposited: 5.0 ETH (locked)\n  ETH Reserve Available: 5.0 ETH (for adding collateral)\n  Loan Amount: $9,000 USD\n  LTV: 60% initial, 75% max, 82.5% liquidation\n  Term: 30 days (2025-01-01 → 2025-01-31)\n  Interest: 5% APR variable\n\nCONTRACTS (4):\n  1. ETH-COLLATERAL-LOCKED: 5.0 ETH locked in loan (CLM)\n  2. ETH-RESERVE-AVAILABLE: 5.0 ETH available for adding (CLM)\n  3. LOAN-USD-9000: $9,000 borrowed (PAM with prepayment)\n  4. TREASURY-CASH: USD cash management (PAM with SCF)\n\nBEHAVIORAL ACTIONS (from Phase 2 derived):\n  Day 12 Noon: Add collateral OR Pay off USD\n  Day 17 6PM: Add collateral OR Pay off USD\n\nTWO-PASS ARCHITECTURE:\n  Phase 0: Load ETH price + rate indexes\n  Phase 1: Register prepayment + LTV models  \n  Phase 2: Asset-only run → derive ETH additions & USD payoffs\n  Phase 3: Register derived SCF models for treasury\n  Phase 4: Full consolidated simulation\n\nTRACKING:\n  - ETH locked (collateral)\n  - ETH available (reserve)\n  - ETH total (portfolio)\n  - USD borrowed\n  - USD cash balance\n  - Net worth (ETH value + USD cash - USD debt)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
